snippet.title: Pt. 1: Who Killed Amber Berbiglia? - Crime Watch Daily with Chris Hansen
snippet.description:
It's a horrifying sight: A woman's dead body is found near her car under a freeway underpass. She wasn't robbed or sexually assaulted, and her phone, keys, and wallet were left untouched. It's a mystery that has baffled her family for years: Who killed Amber Berbiglia, and why?

Check your local listings at http://crimewatchdaily.com/page/2015/06/03/when-its-on/
